           05  w-exe-dat-exe              pic  9(07)                  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Parametri in input estratti                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  w-exe-cod-ubi              pic  x(07)                  .
           05  w-exe-num-pro              pic  x(07)                  .
           05  w-exe-cnv-pro              pic  9(07)                  .

